translations.settings.navigation.title: Ukuzulazula
translations.settings.navigation.start-last-page.desc: Uma uvula uhlelo lokusebenza, buyisela ikhasi lokugcina owawulibuka.
translations.settings.navigation.start-feeds-last-eve: Bonisa izenzakalo ezilayishwe ngaphambilini kuqala uma uvula izifunza, nezithangiso ezintsha ezivela ngenkinobho. Kuvimbela isifunza ukuthi sigxumele ezenzakalweni zamuva uma kulayisha kabusha.
translations.settings.logging.debug.description: Ibonisa yonke imiyalezo yokungena kuhlanganise ulwazi oluningiliziwe lokulungisa.
translations.settings.danger-zone.title: Indawo Eyingozi
translations.settings.danger-zone.reset-notifications: Lokhu kuzosusa zonke izaziso ezibekwe esitoreji sasendaweni. Izaziso zakho zizolandwa kabusha kuma-relay.
translations.settings.danger-zone.wipe-data.descripti: Lokhu kuzosusa yonke idatha yakho yohlelo lokusebenza yasendaweni futhi kulayishe kabusha uhlelo lokusebenza.

translations.settings.relays.no-relays.description: Awukabi nama-relay alungisiwe. Ama-relay abalulekile ukuze usebenzise i-Nostr.
translations.settings.relays.manual-add: Noma engeza i-relay ngokuzenzela usebenzisa ibhokisi elingezansi
translations.settings.relays.malformed.title: Ukumiswa Kwe-Relay Okungalungile Kutholakele
translations.settings.relays.malformed.description: Uhlu lwakho lwama-relay (uhlobo 10002) lwenziwa iklayenti ye-Nostr enye enamagama amathegi angalungile. Isenzakalo sisebenzisa amathegi e-'relay' esikhundleni samathegi afanele e-'r' ngokwe-protocol ye-Nostr.
translations.settings.relays.malformed.action: Lokhu kungavimbela amanye amaklayenti e-Nostr ukuthi alayishe kahle uhlu lwakho lwama-relay. Chofoza inkinobho engezansi ukuze ulungise ngokuzenzakalelayo futhi ushicilele kabusha uhlu lwakho lwama-relay ngefomathi efanele.
translations.settings.relays.malformed.button: Lungisa Futhi Ushicilele Kabusha Uhlu Lwama-Relay
translations.settings.relays.dm-relays.title: Ama-Relay Wemilayezo Eqondile
translations.settings.relays.dm-relays.description: I-Nostria iyeluleka abasebenzisi be-Nostr ukuthi bangasebenzisi ama-relay ahlukene Wemilayezo Eqondile. Uma ufuna lesi sici esithuthukile, ungasebenzisa iklayenti ye-Nostr ehlukile esisekelayo.
translations.settings.relays.deprecated.title: Isexwayiso Sokudala
translations.settings.relays.deprecated.description: Uhlu lwakho lokulandela luqukethe uhlu lwama-relay. Lokhu sekudala ku-protocol.

translations.settings.privacy.reported.description: Khetha izinhlobo zokuqukethwe okubikiwe ezizofihliwe ngokuzenzakalelayo. Uma okuqukethwe kufihlwe, usengakhetha ukukwembula.
translations.settings.privacy.blocked.title: Ama-Akhawunti Avinjiwe
translations.settings.trust.title: Ukwethemba
translations.settings.trust.enable: Nika amandla Izici Ze-Web of Trust
translations.settings.trust.description: Nika amandla izici ze-Web of Trust usebenzisa ama-assertion athembekile e-NIP-85. Lokhu kukuvumela ukuthi ubone izilinganiso zedumela nezibalo zabasebenzisi ezibalwe abahlinzeki bezinsizakalo abathembekile.
translations.settings.trust.relay.title: I-Relay Yokwethemba
translations.settings.trust.relay.description: Khetha i-relay ezosetshenziselwa ukuthola ama-assertion athembekile e-NIP-85 (izenzakalo zohlobo 30382). Lawa ma-relay ahlinzeka ngezilinganiso ezibalwe njengezibalo zabalandeli, izigaba zabasebenzisi, nezibalo zomsebenzi.
translations.settings.trust.relay.label: I-Relay Yokwethemba
translations.settings.trust.about.title: Mayelana nama-Assertion Athembekile e-NIP-85
translations.settings.trust.about.description: I-NIP-85 ivumela abahlinzeki bezinsizakalo ukuthi babale futhi bashicilele izilinganiso mayelana nabasebenzisi nezenzakalo ezazingaba zindleko kakhulu ukubala kumaklayenti. Lezi zihlanganisa izibalo zabalandeli, izigaba zabasebenzisi, izibalo zokuthunyelwe, izinani ze-zap, nokunye okuningi. Isilungiselelo se-relay sigcinwa ngokwasendaweni futhi asingxenyezwa phakathi kwamadivayisi.

translations.settings.about.title: Mayelana Ne-Nostria
translations.settings.about.description: I-Nostria ibuyisela ukulawula lapho kufanele kube khona: kuwe. Yakha inethiwekhi yakho yomphakathi ngendlela oyifunayo, gcina iphrofayela yakho nedatha ngaphansi kokulawula kwakho, futhi wabelane futhi uhlole indawo engagxilile ephikisana nokucubungulwa kuyilapho kushesha ukujoyina futhi kunobungani ukusetshenziswa. Inethiwekhi Yakho Yomphakathi.
translations.settings.about.what-is.title: Iyini i-Nostria?
translations.settings.about.what-is.p1: I-Nostria iklayenti ye-protocol ye-Nostr, okuyiprotocol yenethiwekhi yomphakathi engagxilile. Ivumela abasebenzisi ukuthi baxhumane futhi babelane ngolwazi ngaphandle kokuncika kuseva emaphakathi.
translations.settings.about.what-is.p2: I-Nostria isebenzisa ukusetshenziswa kwe-protocol ye-Nostr ukuqinisekisa ukungagxili okukhulu nokukwazi ukukhula komhlaba wonke, ngaphandle kokunciphisa isipiliyoni somsebenzisi. Iklayenti yakhelwe ukuthi ibe nesheshayo, iphendule, futhi ibe lula ukuyisebenzisa, igxile ekunikezeni isipiliyoni esihle somsebenzisi.
translations.settings.about.desktop.description: I-Nostria iyatholakala futhi njengohlelo lokusebenza lwe-desktop:
translations.settings.about.more-info.description: Vakashela iwebhusayithi yethu ukuthola ulwazi olwengeziwe, amadokhumenti, nokusekela.
translations.settings.about.credits.title: Ukubonga Nokuqaphela
translations.settings.about.credits.description: Sithanda ukukhipha ukubonga kwethu okujulile kubatshalimali bethu abenze i-Nostria yenzeke:
translations.settings.about.credits.thanks: Siyabonga ngokukholelwa embonweni wethu wokwenza i-protocol ye-Nostr itholakale kubo bonke nokusekela ukuthuthukiswa kwenethiwekhi yomphakathi engagxilile ngempela.
translations.settings.relays.discovery.subtitle: Ama-relay okutholwa asetshenziswa ukuthola abasebenzisi abasha nabalandelayo babo.
translations.settings.relays.discovery.empty: Awukanawo ama-relay okutholwa amisiwe. Engeza ama-relay ukuqalisa ukuhlola i-network.
translations.settings.relays.discovery.add-hint: Engeza i-relay yokutholwa usebenzisa inkinobho engenhla.
translations.settings.relays.observed.title: Ama-Relay Abanjiwe
translations.settings.relays.observed.empty.title: Awukanawo Ama-Relay Abanjiwe
translations.settings.relays.observed.empty.descripti: Njengoba usebenzisa i-Nostria, ama-relay adluliswayo kuzigameko azoqoqwa lapha. Lokhu kukusiza ukuhlola i-network nokulawula izixhumanisi.

translations.settings.relays.nip11.name: Igama
translations.settings.relays.tooltip.user-relays.desc: Lawa ngama-relay akhetha ukuwasebenzisa. Asetshenziswa ukushicilela izigameko nokuthola okuqukethwe kwakho.
translations.settings.relays.tooltip.user-relays.note: Qiniseka ukuthi uzimisele abanye abasebenzisi nabo abaneminye yalawa ma-relay ukuze ukuxhumana kube ngcono.
translations.settings.relays.tooltip.discovery-relays: Ama-relay okutholwa asetshenziselwa ukuthola abasebenzisi abasha nabalandelayo babo kuphela.
Lawa ma-relay awasetshenziselwa ukushicilela izigameko zakho.
